snippet.title: Democracy 4: Console Edition - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the launch trailer for Democracy 4: Console Edition, available now on PS4 (PlayStation 4), Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.
Take on the role of President/Prime Minister and govern the country by choosing its policies, laws, and more in this political simulation game. Transform the country as you see fit, but try to retain enough popularity to get re-elected next time.
